7.2 Filling a rectangle
=======================

While the rectangular mode is active, press вАШiвАЩ to fill the rectangle.
You will be asked to choose a character.  You have those options:

   вАҐ for a regular character like вАШtвАЩ, just type it.
   вАҐ вАШSPCвАЩ or вАШDELвАЩ for a shade of grey вАШ" вЦСвЦТвЦУвЦИ"вАЩ among the 5 available
     in UNICODE.  вАШSPCвАЩ to make it darker and darker.  вАШDELвАЩ to make the
     rectangle lighter and lighter.
   вАҐ вАШC-yвАЩ to chose the first character in the top of the kill ring.

   The above selection is the same as for the flood-fill action (see
*note Flood-fill::).


