7.6 ASCII to UNICODE
====================

The standard base-line вАШUnilineвАЩ (вАШINS s 0вАЩ) or вАШaa2u-rectangleвАЩ (вАШINS s
aвАЩ) conversions may be used to convert ASCII art to UNICODE.  The
original ASCII art may be drawn for instance by the вАШartist-modeвАЩ or the
вАШpicture-modeвАЩ packages.

   To use вАШaa2u-rectangleвАЩ, install the вАШascii-art-to-unicodeвАЩ package
by Thien-Thi Nguyen (RIP), available on ELPA.  вАШUnilineвАЩ does not
requires a dependency on this package, by lazy evaluating any call to
вАШaa2u-rectangleвАЩ.  See
<https://elpa.gnu.org/packages/ascii-art-to-unicode.html>




