11 Hydra or Transient?
**********************

The basic usage of вАШUnilineвАЩ should be easy: just move the point, and
lines are traced.  Change brush to draw thicker lines.

   More complex actions are summoned by the вАШ<insert>вАЩ key, with or
without selection.  This is a single key to remember.  Then a textual
menu is displayed, giving the possible keys continuations and their
meaning.  All that is achieved by the вАШHydraвАЩ or вАШTransientвАЩ libraries,
which are now part of вАШEmacsвАЩ (thanks!).

   The вАШHydraвАЩ and вАШTransientвАЩ libraries offer similar features.  Some
users may prefer one or the other.

   вАШUnilineвАЩ was developed from day one with вАШHydraвАЩ.  вАШTransientвАЩ is a
late addition.

* Menu:

* Selecting Hydra or Transient::
* Instantly selecting Hydra or Transient::
* One-liner menus::
* The Hydra interface::
* The Transient interface::


